{"tid":49434,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唉 今日撞番ex。。。。。。","createTime":"2016-12-21T16:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T05:09:08.000Z","uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e70a2f9ca7d870bd3be19edaac2e489a0f0ee3cf","tid":49434,"uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:53:58.000Z","msg":"已經大半年無見<br />\n個心扑扑，扑扑咁跳<br />\n唔知點解<br />\n我終於明白點解個陣佢唔比我送佢到鋪頭門<br />\n可能...佢一直都承認過我<br />\n又可能佢個陣已經諗住分開<br />\n仲記得個陣係街為左送佢番工而嘈架<br />\n個陣落住好大雨<br />\n佢嬲到自己一個一支箭行得好快<br />\n我就一直跟住佢<br />\n之後我仲好掛住佢<br />\n就係個到一路等一路等，等到佢食晏既時候<br />\n可以陪佢，唉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來愛一個人既時候真係會好盲目<br />\n以為佢點都唔會變，好專一好長情<br />\n會一直愛自己，有時仲會突然問佢愛唔愛自己<br />\n可能有啲人會覺得好煩，但其實只係自己心入面既不安<br />\n好想對方會好好安慰自己<br />\n不過人係會變，就算當初幾快樂都樂<br />\nThings will change,so do people."},{"pid":"ee7c423bcbb4d618622b159f2ece49d9b966e771","tid":49434,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:54:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bf5d36ce399d9a4f7e519f36a1e4b40edd34700","tid":49434,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0525bca940120efe6c2b71b310c065e624c4dfde","tid":49434,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:55:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9e2abc3c1f70c32d7b905d41fc981078e1d63a3","tid":49434,"uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:56:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經大半年無見<br />\n個心扑扑，扑扑咁跳<br />\n唔知點解<br />\n我終於明白點解個陣佢唔比我送佢到鋪頭門口<br />\n可能...佢一直都無承認過我<br />\n又可能佢個陣已經諗住分開<br />\n仲記得個陣係街為左送佢番工而嘈架<br />\n個陣落住好大雨<br />\n佢嬲到自己一個一支箭行得好快<br />\n我就一直跟住佢<br />\n之後我仲好掛住佢<br />\n就係個到一路等一路等，等到佢食晏既時候<br />\n可以陪佢，唉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來愛一個人既時候真係會好盲目<br />\n以為佢點都唔會變，好專一好長情<br />\n會一直愛自己，有時仲會突然問佢愛唔愛自己<br />\n可能有啲人會覺得好煩，但其實只係自己心入面既不安<br />\n好想對方會好好安慰自己<br />\n不過人係會變，就算當初幾快樂都好<br />\nThings will change,so do people.</blockquote>"},{"pid":"036ec26254bddb05bdd65063251e817863a72e1a","tid":49434,"uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉bro<br />\n咁就大半年了"},{"pid":"a3bc2c36ecfddad8cacce13e8ff8d4a0f6fd34b8","tid":49434,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉bro<br />\n咁就大半年了</blockquote><br />\n咁快，呢d女雞黎"},{"pid":"26c84c65328706e4e1dc2c4059934d6b57df7063","tid":49434,"uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉bro<br />\n咁就大半年了</blockquote><br />\n咁快，呢d女雞黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我分左之後一個，呢排又一個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時到番我"},{"pid":"ee48c65720fc1efeb5389dc971a6729748c883f2","tid":49434,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉bro<br />\n咁就大半年了</blockquote><br />\n咁快，呢d女雞黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我分左之後一個，呢排又一個<br />\n<img src=\"/ass